<div class="home">
  <div class="how-to">
    <h2>
      Installation
    </h2>
    <span>
      If you have ruby installed:
    </span>
    <div class="code-block">
      gem install gist
    </div>
    If you're using Bundler:
    <div class="code-block">
      source :rubygems
      gem 'gist'
    </div>
    For OS X, gist lives in Homebrew
    <div class="code-block">
      brew install gist
    </div>
    For FreeBSD, gist lives in ports
    <div class="code-block">
      pkg install gist
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
